# Code Review Standards

## Ownership
- Respect CODEOWNERS; reviewers with domain context required.

## What to Check
- Correctness, tests, security, performance, readability, boundary rules.
- Verify Task DoD checked, docs updated, ADR added if needed.

## Anti-Patterns
- Large PRs with mixed concerns; unexplained `eslint-disable`; dead code.